360
00:15:01,640 --> 00:15:02,670
Did the pierrot have it?

361
00:15:02,670 --> 00:15:03,710
The pierrot.

362
00:15:03,710 --> 00:15:06,310
- Darn. - Did the pierrot have it?

363
00:15:08,250 --> 00:15:09,950
- Did the pierrot have it? - The pierrot.

364
00:15:11,950 --> 00:15:12,950
I can barely reach.

365
