370
00:15:30,070 --> 00:15:31,800
- I thought you had some. - Did someone take them?

371
00:15:31,870 --> 00:15:33,300
He doesn't have any clues.

372
00:15:35,110 --> 00:15:36,140
Is this a clue?

373
00:15:38,040 --> 00:15:39,140
"I..."

374
00:15:39,840 --> 00:15:40,880
"don't have..."

375
00:15:42,280 --> 00:15:43,280
