378
00:15:53,490 --> 00:15:55,030
They don't have any clues in their sacks.

379
00:15:55,060 --> 00:15:56,860
People already took them all.

380
00:15:56,860 --> 00:15:58,200
Yes, they've all been taken.

381
00:15:58,630 --> 00:16:00,530
