386
00:16:10,740 --> 00:16:12,010
I think I get it now.

387
00:16:12,680 --> 00:16:14,450
There aren't any more clues around.

388
00:16:14,510 --> 00:16:16,210
This is too tough to crack.

389
00:16:16,610 --> 00:16:18,520
- There aren't any more clues. - There's nothing to go on.

390
00:16:18,520 --> 00:16:19,680
This is a tough one.

391
00:16:19,850 --> 00:16:21,450
I can't find it anywhere.

392
00:16:21,450 --> 00:16:23,720
This is too tough. I'd never find it.

393
00:16:23,720 --> 00:16:25,390
