398
00:16:42,270 --> 00:16:43,940
- Guys! - What is it?

399
00:16:43,940 --> 00:16:45,140
- Hello. - What?

400
00:16:47,110 --> 00:16:48,310
- What is it? - Hello.

401
00:16:48,310 --> 00:16:49,950
- No way! - Hello.

402
00:16:49,950 --> 00:16:50,980
It's Park Shin Yang.

403
00:16:50,980 --> 00:16:52,020
Gosh, hello.

404
00:16:52,020 --> 00:16:56,150
I'll say it, even if I'm nervous

405
00:16:56,350 --> 00:16:59,660
I'll find the courage

406
00:16:59,720 --> 00:17:06,030
Can I love you from today on?

407
00:17:06,030 --> 00:17:10,130
It's my first time

408
00:17:10,130 --> 00:17:13,400
I don't want to lose this feeling

409
00:17:13,470 --> 00:17:17,140
Love must be on its way

410
00:17:17,270 --> 00:17:24,280
I'll give you the very best in life

411
00:17:24,380 --> 00:17:26,080
- Gosh, hello. - He's actually here.

412
00:17:26,080 --> 00:17:27,520
- No way. - Was he here all along?

413
00:17:27,920 --> 00:17:29,220
How is he here?

414
00:17:29,220 --> 00:17:30,220
- Shin Yang! - No way.

415
00:17:30,420 --> 00:17:31,490
No way.

416
00:17:31,790 --> 00:17:32,790
Did you find it?

417
00:17:32,860 --> 00:17:33,860
- What... - No way!

418
00:17:35,190 --> 00:17:36,590
- We haven't found it. - Did you find it?

419
00:17:36,590 --> 00:17:37,760
