420
00:17:37,760 --> 00:17:38,960
Don't you dare!

421
00:17:39,030 --> 00:17:41,060
- Shin Yang! - It's nice to see you.

422
00:17:41,060 --> 00:17:43,800
- Shin Yang, have you been well? - It's been so long.

423
00:17:44,400 --> 00:17:46,370
- Did you find it? Yes, hello. - Hello.

424
00:17:46,370 --> 00:17:47,910
- Your work is amazing! - Exactly.

425
00:17:47,910 --> 00:17:49,140
They're incredible.

426
00:17:49,140 --> 00:17:50,870
I can't believe we're seeing them in person.

427
00:17:51,180 --> 00:17:52,340
Your work is amazing.

428
00:17:52,340 --> 00:17:53,780
- Thank you. - They're incredible.

429
00:17:53,780 --> 00:17:55,550
I think he has a clue.

430
00:17:55,550 --> 00:17:57,010
- Right, a clue. - Shin Yang, is that a clue?

431
00:17:57,010 --> 00:17:58,780
- You haven't found it, have you? - No.

432
00:17:58,780 --> 00:18:00,850
- It's not easy. - Then,

433
