504
00:20:21,120 --> 00:20:22,460
"I didn't go to kindergarten."

505
00:20:23,160 --> 00:20:25,300
- It was sad. - I didn't go to one either.

506
00:20:25,830 --> 00:20:27,130
My parents didn't let me.

507
00:20:28,270 --> 00:20:29,800
Today's race...

508
00:20:30,030 --> 00:20:32,940
is Detective Agency: Find the Genuine Piece.

509
00:20:33,440 --> 00:20:35,340
During the preliminary mission,

510
00:20:35,340 --> 00:20:36,940
you found paintings and clues...

511
00:20:36,940 --> 00:20:38,740
