513
00:20:41,010 --> 00:20:42,050
The paintings?

514
00:20:42,050 --> 00:20:44,480
One of them wasn't for children.

515
00:20:44,480 --> 00:20:45,920
I already have a lot of them.

516
00:20:45,920 --> 00:20:47,320
One is an original piece.

517
00:20:47,320 --> 00:20:48,350
One of them is authentic.

518
00:20:48,350 --> 00:20:49,890
I can narrow it down with the clues I have.

519
00:20:49,890 --> 00:20:52,320
- That's "Judith I." - Just look at that.

520
00:20:52,320 --> 00:20:53,660
With Jae Seok's face...

521
00:20:53,660 --> 00:20:54,930
- Is that Ye Eun? - She looks like someone else.

522
00:20:54,930 --> 00:20:56,860
- That doesn't look like her. - That doesn't look like me.

523
00:20:56,860 --> 00:20:58,500
This is Granny Jee Seok Soon.

524
00:20:58,700 --> 00:21:00,330
- Jee Seok Soon? - Jee Seok Soon.

525
00:21:00,330 --> 00:21:02,770
Why were these kinds of paintings...

526
00:21:02,770 --> 00:21:04,400
- all given to Jong Kook? - Tell me about it.

527
00:21:04,500 --> 00:21:05,570
Hold on.

528
00:21:05,740 --> 00:21:06,940
All the embarrassing ones...

529
00:21:06,940 --> 00:21:09,210
How many of these are there?

530
00:21:09,410 --> 00:21:11,740
- I saw a lot of them. - Why have you stripped me naked?

531
00:21:12,980 --> 00:21:14,750
Did the leaf have to be pointing that way?

532
00:21:16,280 --> 00:21:18,220
I mean, the leaf could point down.

533
00:21:18,220 --> 00:21:20,280
- The leaf is pretty big. - That's not it.

534
00:21:20,280 --> 00:21:22,620
Why are you criticizing a masterpiece?

535
00:21:22,620 --> 00:21:25,120
The leaf is pointing up at an awkward angle.

536
00:21:25,120 --> 00:21:26,860
- Seriously. - What on earth is this?

537
00:21:26,860 --> 00:21:28,430
- That's scary. - Are you kidding me?

538
00:21:28,430 --> 00:21:30,660
- What's that? - They think too highly of you.

