00:21:30,660 --> 00:21:32,860
The leaf could've been much smaller.

540
00:21:34,400 --> 00:21:35,730
- It's too big. - Hold on.

541
00:21:35,730 --> 00:21:37,070
Is one of these an original piece?

542
00:21:37,070 --> 00:21:38,540
There's no way.

543
00:21:38,540 --> 00:21:40,470
- So, - This is going to be tough.

544
00:21:40,470 --> 00:21:41,940
you found clues...

545
00:21:41,940 --> 00:21:43,540
