565
00:22:18,210 --> 00:22:19,610
Me?

566
00:22:19,610 --> 00:22:21,180
Baby, let's go.

567
00:22:21,850 --> 00:22:25,920
For nearly 14 years, he has worked on his art.

568
00:22:26,920 --> 00:22:28,020
- Shin Yang, hi. - Hello.

569
00:22:28,020 --> 00:22:29,890
- Hello. - He's Painter Park now.

570
00:22:29,890 --> 00:22:32,320
- Painter Park. - My gosh.

571
00:22:32,320 --> 00:22:33,390
- Hello. - Hello.

572
00:22:33,390 --> 00:22:35,190
