573
00:22:35,190 --> 00:22:37,030
- You're amazing. - Baby, let's go.

574
00:22:37,030 --> 00:22:38,800
- I mean... - Yes?

575
00:22:38,800 --> 00:22:42,100
A lot of us, myself included,

576
00:22:42,100 --> 00:22:44,030
know that...

577
00:22:44,030 --> 00:22:45,870
- Right. - you're now a painter.

578
00:22:46,040 --> 00:22:47,970
But getting to see your work in person...

579
00:22:48,410 --> 00:22:50,670
- I didn't expect them to be so big. - They're so grand.

580
00:22:50,870 --> 00:22:52,180
They're on another level.

581
00:22:52,180 --> 00:22:55,210
