It'd be fun if Seok Jin played a pierrot.

610
00:23:53,400 --> 00:23:54,870
- Seok Sam's a good choice. - Right.

611
00:23:54,870 --> 00:23:56,170
- That'd be fun. - He'd actually do a good job.

612
00:23:56,170 --> 00:23:57,510
- He'll do a good job. - He'll handle it well.

613
00:23:57,570 --> 00:23:58,610
He has the nose for it.

614
00:23:58,610 --> 00:24:00,710
- I recommend Haha. - Yes?

615
00:24:00,710 --> 00:24:02,250
- He has the nose for it. - Seok Jin.

616
00:24:02,880 --> 00:24:03,910
Me?

617
00:24:03,910 --> 00:24:04,920
Me?

618
00:24:04,920 --> 00:24:06,720
He chose Se Chan. Nice.

619
00:24:10,250 --> 00:24:11,690
- He was able... - Earlier,

620
00:24:11,690 --> 00:24:13,760
- to communicate with them. - he talked to them.

621
00:24:14,420 --> 00:24:15,430
He talked to them.

622
00:24:15,430 --> 00:24:17,930
- He was talking to them earlier. - He'd do a good job.

623
00:24:17,960 --> 00:24:19,800
He can even communicate with them.

624
00:24:20,830 --> 00:24:22,570
