683
00:26:12,540 --> 00:26:13,940
- Me? - Yes.

684
00:26:13,940 --> 00:26:15,210
I must pick Shin Yang first.

685
00:26:15,210 --> 00:26:16,910
- You should. - Right?

686
00:26:16,910 --> 00:26:18,080
- Okay. - Shin Yang.

687
00:26:18,080 --> 00:26:20,050
- You chose Painter Park? - Yes.

688
00:26:20,050 --> 00:26:21,520
Then I'll pick Painter Kim.

689
00:26:21,520 --> 00:26:22,790
- Okay! - Painter Kim.

690
00:26:22,790 --> 00:26:24,350
- Okay. - Then...

691
00:26:24,350 --> 00:26:25,720
- Rock-paper-scissors. - Rock-paper-scissors.

692
00:26:26,960 --> 00:26:28,290
- If you pick Haha... - Do it.

693
00:26:28,290 --> 00:26:29,790
- I'll take Painter Ha. - Painter Ha.

694
00:26:29,790 --> 00:26:31,060
- Okay! - Painter Ha.

695
00:26:31,060 --> 00:26:33,530
- They have Shin Yang. - You have Shin Yang.

696
00:26:33,530 --> 00:26:35,230
- As a painter... - You have Shin Yang.

697
00:26:35,230 --> 00:26:36,830
Yes, that's right.

698
00:26:36,830 --> 00:26:38,600
- Yes. - Rock-paper-scissors.

699
00:26:38,800 --> 00:26:40,440
I should've chosen Shin Yang.

700
00:26:40,440 --> 00:26:41,440
- Okay. - Okay.

701
00:26:41,440 --> 00:26:43,540
The guesser has to do well too.

702
00:26:43,540 --> 00:26:44,940
It requires wit and sense.

703
00:26:44,940 --> 00:26:46,940
Let the opposing team decide the seating order.

704
00:26:46,940 --> 00:26:48,040
Okay.

705
00:26:48,180 --> 00:26:50,250
Put Jae Seok first to ruin the drawing.

706
00:26:50,250 --> 00:26:51,720
If Jong Kook patches it up,

707
00:26:51,720 --> 00:26:52,980
- Ji Hyo can ruin it. - Yes.

708
00:26:52,980 --> 00:26:54,720
- I go first? - I go last?

709
00:26:54,720 --> 00:26:55,790
Have a go.

710
00:26:55,790 --> 00:26:57,990
Those two draw so well.

711
00:26:58,420 --> 00:27:00,190
Let's draw something recognizable.

712
00:27:00,190 --> 00:27:02,430
Yes. The answer... It's not about drawing well.

713
00:27:02,430 --> 00:27:03,530
Right.

714
00:27:03,530 --> 00:27:05,060
You must give clues.

715
00:27:05,060 --> 00:27:07,100
