717
00:27:09,830 --> 00:27:11,940
- That's a long time. - Isn't that too long?

718
00:27:11,940 --> 00:27:12,970
It's short.

719
00:27:12,970 --> 00:27:14,470
I finish in about three seconds.

720
00:27:14,470 --> 00:27:16,570
We'll see. See how things go.

721
00:27:16,570 --> 00:27:17,710
He's so confident.

722
00:27:17,710 --> 00:27:19,280
- I just draw. - Sure, go ahead.

723
00:27:19,280 --> 00:27:22,880
We'll start the mission. Ready, go.

724
00:27:23,250 --> 00:27:24,410
- Gosh... - That?

725
00:27:24,550 --> 00:27:25,620
This is...

726
