735
00:27:39,260 --> 00:27:41,230
Didn't I do pretty well? I did well.

736
00:27:41,230 --> 00:27:43,470
- You did well? - You should've made it bigger.

737
00:27:44,230 --> 00:27:45,300
- I did well. - Pass it on.

