778
00:29:13,420 --> 00:29:15,360
We should swap, right? Swap seats.

779
00:29:15,360 --> 00:29:16,790
- Ji Hyo, you're in. - I'll guess, then.

780
00:29:16,790 --> 00:29:18,530
- Yes. - I'll guess.

781
00:29:18,530 --> 00:29:20,630
- You got much better at drawing. - Didn't I?

782
00:29:20,630 --> 00:29:22,530
Running Man greatly helped improve my skills.

783
00:29:22,530 --> 00:29:24,830
How did you draw the cockroach? It was so well-drawn.

784
00:29:24,830 --> 00:29:26,340
- Wasn't it? - It was nice.

785
00:29:26,740 --> 00:29:28,970
