791
00:29:39,180 --> 00:29:41,080
- What... - What on earth?

792
00:29:41,420 --> 00:29:43,620
I can tell that Jae Seok messed up.

793
00:29:43,620 --> 00:29:45,190
Jae Seok messed up.

794
00:29:45,560 --> 00:29:46,560
He messed up.

795
00:29:46,890 --> 00:29:49,260
- Pass it on. - Pass it on.

796
00:29:49,630 --> 00:29:50,790
- Pass it on. - Pass it on.

797
00:29:50,790 --> 00:29:52,060
Pass it on!

798
00:29:52,130 --> 00:29:53,260
Darn it.

799
00:29:53,260 --> 00:29:55,100
- Well done. - Haha got somewhat closer.

800
00:29:55,100 --> 00:29:57,300
